Àtụ:Infobox badminton player
Ocholi Abel Edicha (amuru 10 Mee 1979) bu onye egwu badminton nke Naijiria
Ọ bụ onye nrite ọla edo nke ụmụ nwoke na 2003 All-Africa Games,  bụkwakwa na mmemme ndi otu agwakọtara na 2007
Ọ gbara asọmpi na 2002 na 2010 Commonwealth Games
Edicha malitere ọrụ ya na badminton mgbe ọ dị obere
Site na nkwado nke nna ya, ọ sonyere n'Enugwu Sports Council
Ndị agha Naijiria were ya n'ọrụ na 1996, ọ nọrọ afọ iri abụọ na atọ
Ọ kwụsịrị ịgbara obodo ya egwuregwu ka 2010 New Delhi Commonwealth Games gachara
